| HistoryText             = The Supreme Four's existence began after the collision of the dimensions caused the members of the [[Supreme Seven (Warp World) (Earth-616)|Supreme Seven]] to merge with each other. The Four helped the [[T'Challa Odinson (Warp World) (Earth-616)|Ghost Hammer]], [[Peter Rogers (Warp World) (Earth-616)|Spider Supreme]], and [[Laura Danvers (Warp World) (Earth-616)|Weapon Peace]] in the battle against [[Mephicthzarrko-Neg (Warp World) (Earth-616)|Mephicthzarrko-Neg, the Tomorrow Demon]] and his summoned minion [[Doomactego (Warp World) (Earth-616)|Doomactego]], but they were hit with another reality-quake which resulted in further amalgamations.

It took the power of [[Hammer Supreme (Warp World) (Earth-616)|the Hammer Supreme]]'s [[Mjolniron]] to repair the damage done to the [[Soul Stone|Soul Gem]] by merging with [[Ezekiel Stane (Warp World) (Earth-616)|Zeke Stane]], which returned everyone back to their original state of being.{{r|Secret Warps: Iron Hammer Annual Vol 1 1}}
